# Syllabus Parser

Turn your syllabus into a study plan and calendar automatically.

## Features

- Upload PDF or DOCX syllabus
- Extracts deadlines (assignments, quizzes, exams, etc.)
- Generates study/prep events
- Creates downloadable calendar (.ics)

## How it works

1. Upload your syllabus  
2. Text is extracted  
3. AI finds important deadlines  
4. Study plan is generated  
5. Download your calendar  

## Tech Stack

- Python
- Streamlit
- OpenAI API
- PyPDF
- python-docx

## Setup

Clone the repo:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/syllabus-parser.git
cd syllabus-parser